  <summary date="2024-08-26T10:45:58Z" status="Introduced in House">Public Inspectors for Safe Infrastructure Act

This bill requires state and local transportation agencies that contract for the construction of federal-aid highways to ensure that a public employee performs the construction inspection functions (such as construction engineering, on-site quality control inspections, and materials testing).&#160;</summary>
